# Specification Change Markers Workflow

Apply this when working in requirement specifications under `spec/requirements/*.md`.

- Accept markers:
  - `[[ADD]] ... [[/ADD]]`
  - `[[REPLACE: "<old snippet>"]] ... [[/REPLACE]]`
  - `[[DELETE: "<old snippet>"]]`
  - `[[NOTE]] ... [[/NOTE]]`
- When user says "implement", first implement code from marked spec content, then integrate markers into clean final spec text.
- Keep wording changes minimal outside marked regions and remove all markers after integration.
